Developed a medical image processing pipeline for processing abdominal CT scans. The pipeline includes a 3D seeded region growing algorithm for semi-automatic tumor segmentation and a manual rigid co-registration system using landmark-based optimization.
<p>Check the full implementation on <a href="https://github.com/abdulaihalidu/Medical-Image-Processing">GitHub</a></p>
